Trip Planner (not confirm!) : A GPS-based mobile application in providing the best and efficient trip.

1 Project Purpose and Scope 

1.1 Project Purpose

The purpose of this project are as follows: 

i) To develop a GPS-based mobile application. 
ii) Learning is the main priority. 
iii) To focus more on technical aspects rather than document. 
iv) To enhance our skill as software developer.


1.2 Project Scope 

The development team will develop an android mobile application to plan an low-cost, efficient trip. The project will focus more on the functionality rather than interface. The project will apply minimum spanning tree algorithm as its core. All team members will use android studio as the developement environment. The project will be complete by Jan 2017. 